are bookstore tucked away in a cozy corner of Shinjuku, complete with its very own adorable cat mascots! In a share bookstore, each shelf is curated by individual "shelf owners," each contributing their own books and personal touch to the space. Inside, you\'ll meet as many fascinating and unique people as there are books: a hairstylist struggling to keep up with the latest trends, a student trying to make ends meet, a bartender eager to understand people through literature, and other colorful patrons seeking the perfect read. Peek into their lives and watch their relationships blossom as they connect over their shared love of books and the stories that bring them together.', 'A Good Day Starts with Cats and Books (Light Novel)', 'A Good Day Starts with Cats and Books Light Novel', 'Satori Satori', 'Airship'], 'author_raw': 'Satori, Satori', 'author': 'Satori Satori', 'ss_title_autocomplete': 'A Good Day Starts with Cats and Books (Light Novel)', 'ss_author_autocomplete': 'Satori Satori', 'suppressed': False, 'deleted': False, 'created_date': '2026-04-29T13:22:56Z', 'publishYear': 2026, 'material_type': 'Book', 'ss_type': 'catalog', 'ss_grouping': 'a-good-day-starts-with-cats-and-books-light-novel-satori-satori-english', 'call_number': '', 'fs_call_number': 0, 'isbn': ['9798895617779', '979-8895617779'], 'language': ['English'], 'summary': ['A cozy bookstore in the corner of Shinjuku is the purrfect escape for those looking for a new story and some furry friends to read with. Welcome to Frere, a picture-purrfect share bookstore tucked away in a cozy corner of Shinjuku, complete with its very own adorable cat mascots! In a share bookstore, each shelf is curated by individual "shelf owners," each contributing their own books and personal touch to the space. Inside, you\'ll meet as many fascinating and unique people as there are books: a hairstylist struggling to keep up with the latest trends, a student trying to make ends meet, a bartender eager to understand people through literature, and other colorful patrons seeking the perfect read. Peek into their lives and watch their relationships blossom as they connect over their shared love of books and the stories that bring them together. \n'], 'is_book_discussion': 0, 'popularity': 11, 'publisher': 'Airship 20260210 ', 'ss_publisher_name': 'Airship', 'available': False, 'collection': ['Titles for Checkout'], 'is_copies': 0, 'is_copies_sort': 0, 'is_holds': 1, 'is_copies_non_deleted': 0, 'is_available_locations': 0, 'bs_all_lib_use_only': False, 'ss_biblevel': 'm', 'sm_bib_varfields': ['100 || {{a}} Satori, Satori', '020 || {{a}} 9798895617779 || {{c}} $15.99', '520 || {{a}} A cozy bookstore in the corner of Shinjuku is the purrfect escape for those looking for a new story and some furry friends to read with. Welcome to Frere, a picture-purrfect share bookstore tucked away in a cozy corner of Shinjuku, complete with its very own adorable cat mascots! In a share bookstore, each shelf is curated by individual "shelf owners," each contributing their own books and personal touch to the space. Inside, you\'ll meet as many fascinating and unique people as there are books: a hairstylist struggling to keep up with the latest trends, a student trying to make ends meet, a bartender eager to understand people through literature, and other colorful patrons seeking the perfect read. Peek into their lives and watch their relationships blossom as they connect over their shared love of books and the stories that bring them together.', '001 ||   in503546648', '260 || {{b}} Airship || {{c}} 20260210', '264 || {{b}} Airship || {{c}} 20260210', '245 || {{a}} A Good Day Starts with Cats and Books (Light Novel)', '008 || 260429s2026                             nam5a '], 'sm_orders': ['1 || Central 1st Fl - Lit Fiction || 2026-04-29', '1 || Dyker Fic || 2026-04-29', '1 || Sunset Pk Fic || 2026-04-29', '1 || Ulmer Park Fic || 2026-04-29', '1 || E Flatbush Fic || 2026-04-29', '1 || Spring Ck Fic || 2026-04-29', '1 || Park Slope Fic || 2026-04-29', '1 || New Utrecht Fic || 2026-04-29'], 'bs_on_order': True, 'ss_marc_tag_001': '  in503546648', '_version_': 1865796489880535040, 'timestamp': '2026-05-21T11:16:32.015Z'}]}}, {'groupValue': 'leave-me-alone-a-good-inside-story-about-deeply-feeling-kids-becky-kennedy-english', 'doclist': {'numFound': 3, 'start': 0, 'numFoundExact': True, 'docs': [{'id': '12925408', 'title': 'Leave me alone! : a good inside story about deeply feeling kids', 'tm_primary_title': ['Leave me alone!'], 'tm_content': ['Emotions.', 'Juvenile works.', 'Novels.', 'Illustrated works.', 'Families.', 'Sensitivity (Personality trait)', 'Human behavior.', 'Conduct of life.', 'Emotions in children.', 'Parent and child', 'Parent and child.', 'Fiction.', 'Picture books.', 'Stone, Joanie,', 'illustrator.', 'https://id.oclc.org/worldcat/entity/E39PCjvcBJDhhb9VQmXTp7fpKb', 'CIPO000336811', "Nothing makes Pia happier than playing secret agents with her brother, Charlie. Until... an unexpected stumble... Did she just ruin the game?! Her body freezes. Her heart pounds. All the feelings in her body start bubbling up, and she explodes. Pia is a Deeply Feeling Kid (DFK). DFKs experience emotions with intensity. Their big reactions to seemingly small events can feel sudden and overwhelming, and attempts to help them often backfire. These are the kids who seem tough and prickly on the outside... yet underneath, they're scared and overwhelmed, struggling to manage feelings that seem too big for their bodies. Parenting a DFK can feel like walking on eggshells-- never sure what might set things off, always bracing for the next explosion. Dr. Becky has created an approach that helps caregivers stay sturdy, build connection, and become the safe base their kid needs-- even in the hardest moments. Picture books from parenting expert Dr. Becky do more than tell a story: They depict real, messy moments and share an important message for kids and parents alike.", 'Good inside story', 'Leave me alone!', '34444963947007', '34444963947015', '34444963947023', '34444963947031', '34444963947049', '34444963947056', '34444963947064', '34444963947072', '34444963947080', '34444963947098', '34444963947106', '34444963947114', '34444963947122', '34444963947130', '34444963947148', '34444963947155', '34444963947163', '34444963947171', '34444963947189', '34444963947197', 'Leave me alone  a good inside story about deeply feeling kids', 'Becky Kennedy', 'Feiwel & Friends', 'A Good Inside Story', 'A Good Inside Story'], 'author_raw': 'Kennedy, Becky (Psychologist), author. https://id.oclc.org/worldcat/entity/E39PCjFkdTfTCWcyR7vHfpjbwK', 'author_alt': 'by Dr. Becky Kennedy ; illustrated by Joanie Stone.', 'author': 'Becky Kennedy', 'ss_title_autocomplete': 'Leave me alone! : a good inside story about deeply feeling kids', 'ss_author_autocomplete': 'Becky Kennedy', 'series': ['Good inside story'], 'ss_od_series': 'A Good Inside Story', 'additional_contributor': ['Stone, Joanie,', 'illustrator.', 'https://id.oclc.org/worldcat/entity/E39PCjvcBJDhhb9VQmXTp7fpKb'], 'opac_label': '', 'suppressed': False, 'deleted': False, 'created_date': '2026-01-16T19:12:42Z', 'publishYear': 2026, 'material_type': 'Book', 'ss_type': 'catalog', 'ss_grouping': 'leave-me-alone-a-good-inside-story-about-deeply-feeling-kids-becky-kennedy-english', 'call_number': 'J-E KENNEDY', 'fs_call_number': 0, 'isbn': ['9781250413116', '978-1250413116', '1250413117', 'CIPO000336811'], 'subjects': ["Children's stories", 'Conduct of life', 'Emotions', 'Emotions in children', 'Families', 'Human behavior', 'Illustrated works', 'Juvenile Literature', 'Parent and child', 'Pictorial works', 'Picture books', 'Psychological aspects', 'Sensitivity (Personality trait)'], 'tm_subject_search': ["Children's stories", 'Conduct of life', 'Emotions', 'Emotions in children', 'Families', 'Human behavior', 'Illustrated works.', 'Juvenile Literature', 'Juvenile fiction.', 'Parent and child', 'Pictorial works', 'Pictorial works.', 'Picture books', 'Picture books.', 'Psychological aspects', 'Sensitivity (Personality trait)'], 'language': ['English'], 'summary': ["Nothing makes Pia happier than playing secret agents with her brother, Charlie. Until... an unexpected stumble... Did she just ruin the game?! Her body freezes. Her heart pounds. All the feelings in her body start bubbling up, and she explodes. Pia is a Deeply Feeling Kid (DFK). DFKs experience emotions with intensity. Their big reactions to seemingly small events can feel sudden and overwhelming, and attempts to help them often backfire. These are the kids who seem tough and prickly on the outside... yet underneath, they're scared and overwhelmed, struggling to manage feelings that seem too big for their bodies. Parenting a DFK can feel like walking on eggshells-- never sure what might set things off, always bracing for the next explosion. Dr. Becky has created an approach that helps caregivers stay sturdy, build connection, and become the safe base their kid needs-- even in the hardest moments. Picture books from parenting expert Dr. Becky do more than tell a story: They depict real, messy moments and share an important message for kids and parents alike. \n"], 'target_age': ['Kids'], 'is_book_discussion': 0, 'available_locations': ['Bushwick Library', 'DeKalb Library', 'Marcy Library'], 'popularity': 32, 'publisher': 'New York : Feiwel & Friends, 2026. ', 'ss_publisher_name': 'Feiwel & Friends', 'available': True, 'collection': ['Titles for Checkout'], 'fiction_status': 'Fiction', 'is_copies': 20, 'is_copies_sort': 20, 'is_holds': 0, 'is_copies_non_deleted': 20, 'is_available_locations': 3, 'bs_all_lib_use_only': False, 'ss_biblevel': 'm', 'sm_item_data': ['{"id":"30264218","updatedDate":"2026-05-12T12:28:43Z","createdDate":"2026-03-10T17:36:00Z","deleted":false,"suppressed":false,"bibIds":["12925408"],"location":{"code":"02jje","name":"Central 1st Fl - Juv J-E"},"status":{"code":"-","display":"CHECK SHELVES","duedate":"2