imestamp': '2026-05-21T18:12:07.946Z'}]}}, {'groupValue': 'hook-up-shaw-hart-english', 'doclist': {'numFound': 1, 'start': 0, 'numFoundExact': True, 'docs': [{'id': '12883448', 'title': 'The hook up', 'tm_primary_title': ['The hook up'], 'tm_content': ['Title from eBook information screen..', "Auden \u200b\u200b\u200b\u200b\u200b\u200b\u200bOpening my own design firm in Lilac Harbor was hard, but things are finally starting to break my way. Then, I meet my new neighbor and the bane of my existence. Wade Collins. He's a grumpy jerk.He's also my partner for a big remodel that I've been hired for. Working with Wade will be difficult, but nothing that I can't handle. Except, the more time that I spend with him, the more that I start to like him. Who knows, maybe by the end of this project, we can even be friends. Wade I've been in love with Auden Laurie since high school. We got off on the wrong foot, though, and I never managed to fix it. Now we're working together, and I know that this is my chance to finally win my girl over. She wants to be friends and bury any hatchets, which is a good start, but I want more. I want all of her. I just need to figure out how to make her mine.", 'Lilac Harbor,', '2.', 'The hook up', 'Lilac Harbor', '2', 'The hook up', 'Shaw Hart', 'Shaw Hart', 'Lilac Harbor', '2'], 'author_raw': 'Hart, Shaw.', 'author_alt': 'Shaw Hart.', 'author': 'Shaw Hart', 'ss_title_autocomplete': 'The hook up', 'ss_author_autocomplete': 'Shaw Hart', 'series': ['Lilac Harbor,', '2.'], 'ss_od_series': 'Lilac Harbor', 'fs_od_reading_order': 2, 'opac_label': 'ONLINE', 'suppressed': False, 'deleted': False, 'created_date': '2025-09-29T15:57:26Z', 'publishYear': 2024, 'material_type': 'eBook', 'ss_type': 'catalog', 'ss_grouping': 'hook-up-shaw-hart-english', 'call_number': 'eBOOK', 'fs_call_number': 0, 'subjects': ['Romance', 'Short Stories'], 'tm_subject_search': ['Fiction.', 'Romance', 'Romance.', 'Short Stories', 'Short Stories.'], 'language': ['English'], 'summary