ah. This was the next good thing. Marcos started taking care of Joe, and in the following months, he discovered Joe had a special gift for helping people find passion, purpose, and meaning in their lives. Ultimately, Marcos realizes Joe helped him much more than he helped Joe. This is Marco\'s inspiring true story of befriending a man near the end of his life who gave him a lasting gift: 10 life-changing lessons to share with others searching for their next good thing." -- from flap of dust jacket.', 'The next good thing', '34444956524110', '34444956524128', '34444956524136', '34444956524144', '34444956524151', '34444956524169', '34444952430114', 'The next good thing  a true story of positivity and transformation in 10 lessons', 'Marcos Prez', 'Union Square & Co.'], 'author_raw': 'Pérez, Marcos, author. https://id.oclc.org/worldcat/entity/E39PCjvXxPWg6wqf8b9kWdvMbm', 'author_alt': 'Marcos Perez and D. Eric Maikranz.', 'author': 'Marcos Pérez', 'ss_title_autocomplete': 'The next good thing : a true story of positivity and transformation in 10 lessons', 'ss_author_autocomplete': 'Marcos Pérez', 'additional_contributor': ['Maikranz, D. Eric', '(David Eric),', '1967-', 'author.', 'https://id.oclc.org/worldcat/entity/E39PBJm9c8WWHTkVgBdGtXxRrq'], 'opac_label': '', 'suppressed': False, 'deleted': False, 'created_date': '2024-09-18T11:31:56Z', 'publishYear': 2024, 'material_type': 'Book', 'ss_type': 'catalog', 'ss_grouping': 'next-good-thing-a-true-story-of-positivity-and-transformation-in-10-lessons-marcos-pérez-english', 'call_number': 'B PEREZ P', 'fs_call_number': 0, 'isbn': ['1454952180', '9781454952183', '978-1454952183'], 'subjects': ['Autobiographies', 'Caregivers', 'Cerebrovascular disease', 'Depressed persons', 'Helping behavior', 'Interpersonal relations', 'Joe Sabah', 'Life change events', 'Marcos Pérez', 'Mindfulness (Psychology)', 'Patients', 'Self-actualization (Psychology)', 'Self-help publications', 'Single parents'], 'tm_subject_search': ['Autobiographies