 and the women find themselves at the heart of a supernatural conspiracy linked to St. Augustine's colonial past. Together, they vow to expose the town's historical sins, but the deeper Jean digs, the less clear it becomes: Who is Cheyenne Rite, and when does a quest for truth become a thirst for vengeance? Curated by award-winning bestselling author Scott Snyder (Batman, We Have Demons), this new installment of the Dark Spaces anthology series features rising talents Che Grayson (Batman: Urban Legends) and Kelsey Ramsay (Joan Jett and the Black Hearts, I Love Rock-n-Roll) as they team up for an eerie historical thriller about obsession, power, and redemption in Dark Spaces: Good Deeds!", 'Dark Spaces: Good Deeds (2023),', '1-6.', 'Dark spaces good deeds', 'Dark Spaces: Good Deeds (2023)', '6', 'Dark spaces good deeds', 'Che Grayson', 'IDW Publishing', 'Dark Spaces: Good Deeds (2023)', '6', 'Dark Spaces: Good Deeds (2023)', '6'], 'author_raw': 'Grayson, Che.', 'author_alt': 'Che Grayson.', 'author': 'Che Grayson', 'ss_title_autocomplete': 'Dark spaces: good deeds', 'ss_author_autocomplete': 'Che Grayson', 'series': ['Dark Spaces: Good Deeds (2023),', '1-6.'], 'ss_od_series': 'Dark Spaces: Good Deeds (2023)', 'fs_od_reading_order': 6, 'opac_label': 'ONLINE', 'suppressed': False, 'deleted': False, 'created_date': '2026-01-09T15:57:28Z', 'publishYear': 2024, 'material_type': 'eBook', 'ss_type': 'catalog', 'ss_grouping': 'dark-spaces-good-deeds-che-grayson-english', 'call_number': 'eBOOK', 'fs_call_number': 0, 'isbn': ['9781649361875', '978-1649361875'], 'subjects': ['Comic and Graphic Books', 'Graphic novels', 'Journalists', 'Paranormal comics', 'Saint Augustine (Fla)', 'Supernatural', 'Teenage girls', 'Thriller comics', 'United States'], 'tm_subject_search': ['Comic and Graphic Books', 'Comic and Graphic Books.', 'Fiction.', 'Graphic novels', 'Journalists', 'Paranormal comics', 'Saint Augustine (Fla)', 'Supernatural', 'Teenage girls', 'Thriller comics', 'United States