n I convince her that she is enough? This book comes with the promise of a happily ever after, a steamy sex scene, no cliffhangers, and no cheating. Read this story if you're ready to fall in love at a library and laugh along the way.", 'Paws up for the dad bod', 'Paws up for the dad bod', 'Elsie James', 'Elsie James'], 'author_raw': 'James, Elsie.', 'author_alt': 'Elsie James.', 'author': 'Elsie James', 'ss_title_autocomplete': 'Paws up for the dad bod', 'ss_author_autocomplete': 'Elsie James', 'opac_label': 'ONLINE', 'suppressed': False, 'deleted': False, 'created_date': '2024-02-09T20:45:11Z', 'publishYear': 2024, 'material_type': 'eBook', 'ss_type': 'catalog', 'ss_grouping': 'paws-up-for-the-dad-bod-elsie-james-english', 'call_number': 'eBOOK', 'fs_call_number': 0, 'isbn': ['9798223762461', '979-8223762461'], 'subjects': ['Humor (Fiction)', 'Romance', 'Short Stories'], 'tm_subject_search': ['Fiction.', 'Humor (Fiction).', 'Romance.', 'Short Stories.'], 'language': ['English'], 'summary': ["Single Dad librarian & Veterinarian romance with a cute kid and a grumpy cat. Get ready to fall in love!  Suri  I always thought I'd be a mom, it would've been a natural fit for me. So when I found out that I can't have children, I was shocked. When my husband left me because of it, I was devastated. It's been five years since then and I've worked hard to start a new life. I went back to school and landed my dream job as a veterinarian. The animals are my babies now. But when volunteering at our local library puts me in contact with a smoking hot dad bod, everything goes paws up. Silas is sexy, charming, and I want to write a new chapter with him. But can I convince him that love lasts forever?  Silas  When I lost my wife, I lost everything... Except for my little girl, Tilly. Being a single dad isn't something I ever planned on, but I'm making it work. Moving back to my small hometown to take a job at the local library seems like a good place to start. But when a veterinarian